	<h1><ul id="NavMenu"><li><a href="{{ path('ComppiDescriptionBundle_help') }}">Help</a></li><li>Input Databases</li></ul></h1>
	
	<p>ComPPI is an integrated database merging 10 protein-protein interaction and 9 subcellular localization databases. The resources are freely avaiable for academical research, and allows proteom-wide download options. The input databases are connected to the ComPPI database via input database specific interfaces. To learn more about how we deal with different protein naming conventions and subcellular localizations click <a name="namingconventions">here</a> or <a name="#subcellocs">here</a>.</p>
	<p></p>
	
